quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  40,34,aur pehlay Yousuf bhi tumahray paas nishanain le kar aeye they to jo woh laaye they is se tum hamesha shak hi mein rahay. yahan taq ke jab woh faut hogaye to tum kehnay lagey ke khuda is ke baad kabhi koi paighambar nahi beje ga. isi terhan khuda is shakhs ko gumraah kar deta hai jo hadd se nikal jaane wala aur shak karne wala ho
  40,35,jo log baghair is ke ke un ke paas koi Daleel aayi ho khuda ki aayton mein jhagarte hain. khuda ke nazdeek aur mominoun ke nazdeek yeh jhagra sakht napasand hai. isi terhan khuda har mutaqabbir sarkash ke dil par mohar laga deta hai
  40,36,aur firaon ne kaha ke Haman mere liye aik mehal banaao taakay mein ( is par charh kar ) rustoon par poanch jaoon
  40,37,"( yani ) asmano ke rustoon par, phir moose ke khuda ko dekh lon aur mein to usay jhoota samjhta hon. aur isi terhan firaon ko is ke aamaal bad achay maloom hotay they aur woh raste se rok diya gaya tha. aur firaon ki tadbeer to be car thi"
  40,38,aur woh shakhs jo momin tha is ne kaha ke bhayio mere peechay chalo mein tumhe bhalai ka rasta dikhao n
  40,39,bhayio yeh duniya ki zindagi ( chand roza ) faida uthany ki cheez hai. aur jo akhirat hai wohi hamesha rehne ka ghar hai
  40,40,jo buray kaam kere ga is ko badla bhi waisa hi miley ga. aur jo naik kaam kere ga mard ho ya aurat aur woh sahib imaan bhi hoga to aisay log bahisht mein daakhil hon ge wahan un ko be shumaar rizaq miley ga
